Jimmy Bullard opted to head for the jungle after losing £625,000 in an investment scheme.

The former Fulham midfielder – who retired two years ago following a series of crippling knee injuries – is among 10 famous faces to descend on Australia for the annual I’m A Celebrity… Get Me Out Of Here! show.

But his appearance is down to monetary concerns rather than a thirst for publicity, reports The Sun.

