Bullard, who at the height of his earning power took home £45,000 a week at Hull, will pocket around £100,000 for his appearance Down Under as he bids to recoup some cash sunk in the scheme.

A number of Premier League stars, including ex-Tottenham striker Robbie Keane, are said to have lost out.

